1  ng new Movie time - to create project
2  run angular - ng s -o
3  index.html
      add bootstrap
      add font awesome- (font awesome cdn), goodle font
4  lazy loading    
      its a process of loading components and modules
      it improves application load time and performance 

      ng g m movies --route movies --module app.module

5  create a component lazy loaded in the movie module 
              all-movies - ng g c movies/all-movies
              your-shows - ng g c movies/your-shows
6  set up path for each module
          movies-routing module
7  pageNotFound - ng g c page-not-found       
     setting path for page-not-found - app-routing.module
8  creating header vand footer 
     ng g c header
     ng g c footer   
9  designing of frontend
10  integration  
    a)  creating service for API call -  ng g s movies/api
    b)  import HttpClientModule in movie module
    c)  dependency injection HttpClient class in API services